ite may offer drug testing and education and employment verification, while another offers just a simple background check. Knowing what type of information you want to find out about an applicant will help you decide what type of screening you need done and what service you want it done by.","<strong>Turnaround Time</strong><br/>Depending on how soon you need the results of your screenings, you will prefer one site to the other. Some sites allow you to search and view results instantly while others may take a minimum of a day and up to three days at maximum to get your results back. When making a decision for hiring someone, you may not always have the time to wait three days to get results back, so the sooner the better.","<strong>Customization</strong><br/>It is important that you get all of the options for screenings and reports that you want. Some services only offer certain packages while others start with packages but allow for customization. You should make sure that you can receive the information you want.","Choosing which employment screening service to go with can be an easy decision if you now what type of screenings and tests you want done and how fast you need the results. While some offer a variety of tests, they may take a longer time to get your results. The site you pick is ultimately dependent upon your employment needs."]},"id":"67668d75-a46f-4a80-91c2-ace29a678022","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Related Product Reviews"},"id":"39550da0-a1b0-4b96-a200-4d59ad237752","type":"heading"},{"data":{"items":["<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/hr-personnel/employee-background-checks/rfqz/?publisherId=21232&publisherTypeId=1788&keywordID=EmploymentScreeningServices\">Background Report</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/hr-personnel/employee-background-checks/rfqz/?publisherId=21232&publisherTypeId=1788&keywordID=EmploymentScreeningServices\">Corra Group</a>","<a href=\"http://www.buyerzone.com/hr-personnel/employee-background-checks/rfqz/?publisher